ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR BEATSCHAIN PLATFORM:

1. MUSIC LICENSING: All beats uploaded to the BeatsChain platform remain the 
   intellectual property of their respective creators. The platform facilitates 
   licensing agreements between producers and buyers.

2. NFT OWNERSHIP: NFT ownership grants specific usage rights as defined in the 
   individual beat's license terms, not copyright ownership of the underlying 
   musical work.

3. ROYALTY OBLIGATIONS: All parties must respect the automated royalty 
   distribution system implemented in the smart contracts.

4. PLATFORM FEES: The platform reserves the right to collect reasonable fees 
   for facilitating transactions and maintaining the service.

5. COMPLIANCE: Users must comply with all applicable copyright laws and 
   licensing requirements in their jurisdiction.